Honestly this post is really really concerning. If you're a person suffering with any of these problems, there are resources on campus to help you. Cal offers free counseling services if you have SHIP, and else you get 5 counseling appointments (plus 3 extra with a $15 co-pay) and will be referred to a professional on your insurance plan. I recommend giving counseling/therapy a chance, because these professionals are dedicated to making sure our lives are okay! https://uhs.berkeley.edu/counseling/appointments
